{
 "name": "RPlog_Jedi_Purge_-_Cort_versus_Ethan",
 "title": "Jedi Purge: Cort versus Ethan",
 "summary": "Having already killed Aubrey, Priti, and Tholt, the corrupted apprentice Cort rigs the Tatooine Jedi School with a bomb and lies in wait as the last surviving student, Ethan, returns on a Dewback with the protocol droid Threepio and a recovered statue. Stricken with grief at the sight of his dead friends, Ethan is ambushed: Cort blasts Threepio and crushes Ethan's dog Bram against a wall with the Force before the two duel with lightsabers amid the wreckage. Driven into an animal rage by Ethan calling him 'Cort,' the Dark Jedi overwhelms the half-blind apprentice and beats him to death. With the bomb's timer ticking down, Cort gathers his trophies and leaves the school behind, content to return home to his master.",
